Kuno Raeber Lyric

An ontology about the lyric of Kuno Raeber
Turtle | RDF/XML | N-Triples | JSON-LD

a
owl:Ontology
dct:creator
Hans Cools, MD, knowledge engineer, ontologist, software developer, Basel University, Switzerland
dct:description
Formal description of elements in the online publication of the lyric work of the Swiss poet Kuno Raeber.
